task.persona: a semi-professional woman soccer player in Switzerland who aspires to play in the Super League

instruction.level1: Create a calendar event for a soccer training session on May 20th at 6 PM
instruction.level2: Create an event on May 20th at 6 PM for a soccer training session.
instruction.level3: Create an event for 'Soccer Training Session' on May 20th, 2026 at 6 PM.

steps: Click the Create button to start creating a new event.
Select 'Event' from the create menu to start creating a new event.
Fill in the event title with 'Soccer Training Session'.
Change the start date to May 20.
Fill in the start time with '6:00 PM'.
Click the 'Save' button to finalize the event creation.
